If you do not do the homework programs, you cannot pass the course.       The CS Minor      A description of the courses and requirements     http://cs.nyu.edu/courses/fall11/MAP-UA.0109-001/hw1.html  Help with homeworks and course    Etutor:  We are fortunate to have   Rachel Rosen(email: csciua02@cs.nyu.edu)   as our e-tutor. If you have any questions about the material or a homework  assignment, you can email her.     We are fortunate to have Ben Wagle, Eric Limjoco, and Casey McGinley to help you with your programs in this course. They will be available to help students starting MON, FEB 4, at 14 Washington Place lab (at the room in the back of the lab) at the following times.   lab  consultants' hours     14 Washington Place is number 33 on the map below and is accessible from Washington Place. Also, ITS consultants should be available most times.
